                <p class="privacy-cookies">For <em>Microsoft Internet Explorer</em>:</p>
                <p class="privacy-cookies">1. Choose the menu “tools” then “Internet Options”</p>
                <p class="privacy-cookies">2. Click on the “privacy” tab</p>
                <p class="privacy-cookies">3. Select the appropriate setting</p>
                <p class="MsoNormal">For <em>Microsoft Edge</em>:</p>
